&lt;p&gt;Pennine Care NHS Foundation Trust&lt;br /&gt;CONSULTANT (INPATIENTS) GENERAL ADULT PSYCHIATRY&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pennine Care NHS Foundation Trust is looking to recruit a 1 WTE Consultant ( inpatients ) in General Adult psychitry for Rochdale. Moorside ward one of 2 inpatient wards based at the John Elliot unit Birch Hill Hospital Rochdale. . The post is a well established post and provides inpatient care for acutely unwell patients living in the Rochdale bororugh (HMR). This post will be based at Birch Hill Hospital (BHH), Rochdale. Rochdale operates an Inpatient-Outpatient model (New ways of working) and is staffed by 7 full-time Consultants in General Adult, 2 full time Old age psychiatrist and 1 in intellectual disability. Junior doctors are allocated (HEENW training scheme) to work with the consultants.Applicants must be on the GMC&#39;s specialist register or anticipated award of CCT within 3 months.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Ema Etuk&lt;br /&gt;BHH, Rochdale&lt;br /&gt;OL12 9QB&lt;br /&gt;Tel 01706 676252&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Caroline Mccann, Borough Mental Health Offices&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Birch Hill Hospital Rochdale OL12 9RD, Tel 01706 54316&lt;/p&gt;
